name: Monsters Series. Drunky Monster #5
description: A Happy Monster, walking along the city, soon to be killed by a bus!... like to add it to your collection?. A series of monsters which will be minted in two different blockchains as a cross-platform experiment. Already four, three here in Tezos at https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/tz/tz1XQaUFFRCNAAaiX6vgqkCL8c7oGqB9WQ76 , the other two at https://opensea.io/collection/kryptoticons. In all cases, edition 33. If you want the full series, will have to buy in different blockchains. Enjoy!
